 the tribe of the children of Nephthali.","searchKeywords":["this","the","inheritance","tribe","children","nephthali"]},{"verseId":"brenton_joshua_19_40","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":6,"bookName":"Joshua","bookAbbrev":"joshua","chapter":19,"verse":40,"text":"And the seventh lot came out to Dan.","searchKeywords":["and","the","seventh","lot","came","out","dan"]},{"verseId":"brenton_joshua_19_41","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":6,"bookName":"Joshua","bookAbbrev":"joshua","chapter":19,"verse":41,"text":"And their borders were Sarath, and Asa, and the cities of Sammaus,","searchKeywords":["and","their","borders","were","sarath","asa","the","cities","sammaus"]},{"verseId":"brenton_joshua_19_42","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":6,"bookName":"Joshua","bookAbbrev":"joshua","chapter":19,"verse":42,"text":"and Salamin, and Ammon, and Silatha,","searchKeywords":["and","salamin","ammon","silatha"]},{"verseId":"brenton_joshua_19_43","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":6,"bookName":"Joshua","bookAbbrev":"joshua","chapter":19,"verse":43,"text":"and Elon, and Thamnatha, and Accaron;","searchKeywords":["and","elon","thamnatha","accaron"]},{"verseId":"brenton_joshua_19_44","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":6,"bookName":"Joshua","bookAbbrev":"joshua","chapter":19,"verse":44,"text":"and Alcatha, and Begethon, and Gebeëlan,","searchKeywords":["and","alcatha","begethon","gebe","lan"]},{"verseId":"brenton_joshua_19_45","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":6,"bookName":"Joshua","bookAbbrev":"joshua","chapter":19,"verse":45,"text":"and Azor, and Banæbacat, and Gethremmon.","searchKeywords":["and","azor","ban","bacat","gethremmon"]},{"verseId":"brenton_joshua_19_46","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":6,"bookName":"Joshua","bookAbbrev":"joshua","chapter":19,"verse":46,"text":"And westward of Hieracon the border near to Joppa.","searchKeywords":["and","westward","hieracon","the","border","near","joppa"]},{"verseId":"brenton_joshua_19_47","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":6,"bookName":"Joshua","bookAbbrev":"joshua","chapter":19,"verse":47,"text":"This the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Dan, according to their families, these their cities and their villages:","searchKeywords":["this","the","inheritance","tribe","children","dan","according","their","families","these","cities","and","villages"]},{"verseId":"brenton_joshua_19_48","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":6,"bookName":"Joshua","bookAbbrev":"joshua","chapter":19,"verse":48,"text":"edge of the sword; and they dwelt in it, and called the name of it Lasendan:","searchKeywords":["edge","the","sword","and","they","dwelt","called","name","lasendan"]},{"verseId":"brenton_joshua_19_51","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":6,"bookName":"Joshua","bookAbbrev":"joshua","chapter":19,"verse":51,"text":"the divisions which Eleazar the priest divided by lot, and Joshua the of Naue, and the heads of families among the tribes of Israel, according to the lots, in Selo before the Lord by the doors of the tabernacle of testimony, and they went to take possession of the land.","searchKeywords":["the","divisions","which","eleazar","priest","divided","lot","and","joshua","naue","heads","families","among","tribes","israel","according","lots","selo","before","lord","doors","tabernacle","testimony","they","went","take","possession","land"]}]